
  libva-vdpau-driver
  A VDPAU-based backend for VA-API

  Copyright (C) 2009-2011 Splitted-Desktop Systems


License
-------

libva-vdpau-driver is available under the terms of the GNU General
Public License.


Overview
--------

libva-vdpau-driver consists in a VDPAU-based backend for VA-API.


Requirements
------------

libVA API version (not package)	GLX support	MPEG-4 support
0.29-branch >= 0.29.0-sds8	No		No
0.30-branch >= 0.30.0-sds1	No		No
0.30-branch >= 0.30.4-sds5	Yes		No
upstream 0.31-branch		No		No
0.31-branch >= 0.31.0-sds1	Yes		No
0.31-branch >= 0.31.0-sds4	Yes		Yes

mplayer-vaapi >= 20090320 patchset is also needed if you intend to use
MPlayer.
